<div class="sub-title">Portfolio</div>
<div class="text">
	<b> GeoStockPhoto </b> provides to the photographers a map with all their photos on sale. <br>
You can reach this page in two ways:
	<ul>
		<li>through the link on your personal page</li>
		<li>through the link www.geostockphoto.com/portfolio/<i>username</i></li>
	</ul>
</div>
<br>
<div class="sub-title">Personal page</div>
<div class="text">
	<b> GeoStockPhoto </b> provides you with a personal page visible to all users and visitors of the site.
	<br>
	The first part is dedicated to all registered users, including:
	<ul>
		<li><b>Your personal photo</b></li>
		<li><b>Personal information</b></li>
		<li><b>Your position</b></li>
	</ul>
	<br>
	A second part is dedicated only to photographers.
	This second part will contain:
	<ul>
		<li><b>Photographer statistics on GeoStockPhoto</b> (at least 10 photos in portfolio required)</li>
		<li><b>Career information submitted by photographer</b> (at least 100 photos in portfolio required)</li>
		<li><b>Contacts and links to other sites of the photographer</b> (at least 1000 photos in portfolio required)</li>
	</ul>
</div>
